room_title: Escape room "Pharaoh's Revenge" by Clue Quest in Oklahoma City
review: We went tonight for the first time! We did the Pharaoh's Revenge room. It was such a fun time. The clues were very well thought out, and while you had to work for them, it wasn't ever frustrating. The people are so nice and enthusiastic, and you can tell they really love what they do. This was the best double date night ever!! The mystery/puzzle nerd in me is fully satisfied.

room_title: Escape room "Pharaoh's Revenge" by Clue Quest in Oklahoma City
review: Awesome time!! Very challenging. Enjoyed every minute! Such friendly owners too cannot wait to come back and try another room.

room_title: Escape room "Pharaoh's Revenge" by Clue Quest in Oklahoma City
review: We tried Clara's room first and had so much fun we went straight to Pharaoh's room. It was so much fun and we won t-shirts!!! We went as a group of 6. Fun times!!
